                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-195-off1166 t18320405-195-crimeloc1169"></join>. On the afternoon of the 26th of March I was in his cellar - I saw the prisoner enter the shop, open a box which was there, and take out three brass wheel caps.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-195-person1746">
                  GEORGE 
                  BALDERY
               <interp inst="t18320405-195-person1746" type="surname" value="BALDERY"></interp>
